# HimRate — Kamal Secrets (common to all destinations)
# Evaluated as shell script. CI sets env vars; local deploys require explicit exports.
#
# SECURITY: KAMAL_REGISTRY_PASSWORD must be a DEDICATED fine-grained PAT
# с scope `read:packages` (и `write:packages` только если локально пушим images).
# НЕ использовать personal `gh auth token` — mixing dev/deploy creds, нельзя
# rotate independently, легко over-scoped. См. docs/runbooks/kamal_local_deploy.md
# для генерации + ротации.
#
# Fail-fast: ВСЕ secrets ниже используют ${VAR:?...} pattern — kamal остановится
# с explicit error если env var не set. Silent fallback (:- или plain $VAR
# passthrough) anti-pattern: missing secret → empty value → app crashes в runtime
# или работает с broken features → debugging nightmare. Fail-fast at deploy time
# локализует ошибку к источнику.
#
# RAILS_MASTER_KEY оставляем с fallback на config/master.key для local dev
# convenience (file gitignored, но существует у developers). CI всегда передаёт
# через env.

KAMAL_REGISTRY_PASSWORD=${KAMAL_REGISTRY_PASSWORD:?must be exported locally — see docs/runbooks/kamal_local_deploy.md для dedicated PAT setup}
RAILS_MASTER_KEY=${RAILS_MASTER_KEY:-$(cat config/master.key)}
POSTGRES_PASSWORD=${POSTGRES_PASSWORD:?required — accessory db init password}
DATABASE_URL=${DATABASE_URL:?required — staging uses secrets.STAGING_DATABASE_URL, prod constructed inline от POSTGRES_PASSWORD}
REDIS_URL=${REDIS_URL:?required — redis://himrate-redis:6379/\{0|1\} (prod/staging)}
JWT_SECRET=${JWT_SECRET:?required — JWT session signing}
SECRET_KEY_BASE=${SECRET_KEY_BASE:?required — Rails session cookies}
TWITCH_CLIENT_ID=${TWITCH_CLIENT_ID:?required — Twitch OAuth app}
TWITCH_CLIENT_SECRET=${TWITCH_CLIENT_SECRET:?required — Twitch OAuth app}
TWITCH_REDIRECT_URI=${TWITCH_REDIRECT_URI:?required — OAuth callback URL (api.himrate.com или staging.himrate.com)}
GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=${GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID:?required — Google OAuth app}
GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=${GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET:?required — Google OAuth app}
GOOGLE_REDIRECT_URI=${GOOGLE_REDIRECT_URI:?required — OAuth callback URL}
ACTIVE_RECORD_ENCRYPTION_PRIMARY_KEY=${ACTIVE_RECORD_ENCRYPTION_PRIMARY_KEY:?required — AR column encryption}
ACTIVE_RECORD_ENCRYPTION_DETERMINISTIC_KEY=${ACTIVE_RECORD_ENCRYPTION_DETERMINISTIC_KEY:?required — AR column encryption}
ACTIVE_RECORD_ENCRYPTION_KEY_DERIVATION_SALT=${ACTIVE_RECORD_ENCRYPTION_KEY_DERIVATION_SALT:?required — AR column encryption}
FLIPPER_UI_PASSWORD=${FLIPPER_UI_PASSWORD:?required — Flipper admin UI basic auth}
FLIPPER_UI_USER=${FLIPPER_UI_USER:?required — Flipper admin UI basic auth}
ALLOWED_EXTENSION_ID=${ALLOWED_EXTENSION_ID:?required — Chrome extension ID для CORS}
TWITCH_WEBHOOK_SECRET=${TWITCH_WEBHOOK_SECRET:?required — EventSub HMAC SHA256 verification}
EVENTSUB_WEBHOOK_URL=${EVENTSUB_WEBHOOK_URL:?required — Twitch EventSub callback URL}
